}};\" |\n| style=\"text-align:left;\" | <small>[[Tim Farron]]</small>\n| style=\"text-align:right;\" | 12\n| style=\"text-align:right;\" | {{Percentage|12|650|1|pad=yes}}\n| data-sort-value=\"\" | {{Infobox political party/seats|12|650|hex={{Liberal Democrats (UK)/meta/color}}}}\n| style=\"text-align:right;\" | 2,371,861\n| style=\"text-align:right;\" | 7.4%\n| {{percentage bar|7.4||c={{Liberal Democrats (UK)/meta/color}}|border-color=#c0c0c0|background-color=#f0f0f0}}\n|-\n| style=\"text-align:left;\" | [[Democratic Unionist Party]]\n| style=\"background:{{Democratic Unionist Party/meta/color}};\" |\n| style=\"text-align:left;\" | <small>[[Arlene Foster]]</small>\n| style=\"text-align:right;\" | 10\n| style=\"text-align:right;\" | {{Percentage|10|650|1|pad=yes}}\n| data-sort-value=\"\" | {{Infobox political party/seats|10|650|hex={{Democratic Unionist Party/meta/color}}}}\n| style=\"text-align:right;\" | 292,316\n| style=\"text-align:right;\" | 0.9%\n| {{percentage bar|0.9||c={{Democratic Unionist Party/meta/color}}|border-color=#c0c0c0|background-color=#f0f0f0}}\n|-\n| style=\"text-align:left;\" | [[Sinn F\u00e9in]]\n| style=\"background:{{Sinn F\u00e9in/meta/color}};\" |\n| style=\"text-align:left;\" | <small>[[Gerry Adams]]</small>\n| style=\"text-align:right;\" | 7\n| style=\"text-align:right;\" | {{Percentage|7|650|1|pad=yes}}\n| data-sort-value=\"\" | {{Infobox political party/seats|7|650|hex={{Sinn F\u00e9in/meta/color}}}}\n| style=\"text-align:right;\" | 238,915\n| style=\"text-align:right;\" | 0.7%\n| {{percentage bar|0.7||c={{Sinn F\u00e9in/meta/color}}|border-color=#c0c0c0|background-color=#f0f0f0}}\n|-\n| style=\"text-align:left;\" | [[Plaid Cymru]]\n| style=\"background:{{Plaid Cymru/meta/color}}\" |\n| style=\"text-align:left;\" | <small>[[Leanne Wood]]</small>\n| style=\"text-align:right;\" | 4\n| style=\"text-align:right;\" | {{Percentage|4|650|1|pad=yes}}\n| data-sort-value=\"\" | {{Infobox political party/seats|4|650|hex={{Plaid Cymru/meta/color}}