g]] <small>(1/6)</small> <sup>'''\u2020\u2020\u2020\u2020'''</sup>||{{flagicon|SWE}} Mats Wilander <small>(4/7)</small>||{{flagicon|FRG}} [[Boris Becker]] <small>(1/6)</small>||{{flagicon|Czechoslovakia}} Ivan Lendl <small>(2/8)</small>\n|-\n|style=\"background:seashell\"|'''[[1986 Grand Prix (tennis)|1986]]'''||style=\"background:#ececec;color:gray;text-align:center\" class=\"table-na\"|<small>Tournament date changed</small>||style=\"background:seashell\"|{{flagicon|Czechoslovakia}} Ivan Lendl <small>(3/8)</small>||{{flagicon|West Germany}} Boris Becker <small>(2/6)</small>||style=\"background:seashell\"|{{flagicon|Czechoslovakia}} Ivan Lendl <small>(4/8)</small>\n|-\n|style=\"background:seashell\"|'''[[1987 Grand Prix (tennis)|1987]]'''||{{flagicon|SWE}} Stefan Edberg <small>(2/6)</small>||style=\"background:seashell\"|{{flagicon|Czechoslovakia}} Ivan Lendl <small>(5/8)</small>||{{flagicon|AUS}} [[Pat Cash]]||style=\"background:seashell\"|{{flagicon|Czechoslovakia}} Ivan Lendl <small>(6/8)</small>\n|-\n|style=\"background:#FFEFD5\"|'''[[1988 Grand Prix (tennis)|1988]]'''||style=\"background:#FFEFD5\"|{{flagicon|SWE}} Mats Wilander <small>(5/7)</small>||style=\"background:#FFEFD5\"|{{flagicon|SWE}} Mats Wilander <small>(6/7)</small>||{{flagicon|SWE}} Stefan Edberg <small>(3/6)</small>||style=\"background:#FFEFD5\"|{{flagicon|SWE}} Mats Wilander <small>(7/7)</small>\n|-\n|style=\"background:seashell\"|'''[[1989 Grand Prix (tennis)|1989]]'''||{{flagicon|Czechoslovakia}} Ivan Lendl <small>(7/8)</small>||{{flagicon|USA}} [[Michael Chang]]||style=\"background:seashell\"|{{flagicon|FRG}} Boris Becker <small>(3/6)</small>||style=\"background:seashell\"|{{flagicon|FRG}} Boris Becker <small>(4/6)</small>\n|-\n|'''[[1990 ATP Tour|1990]]'''||{{flagicon|Czechoslovakia}} Ivan Lendl <small>(8/8)</small>||{{flagicon|ECU}} [[Andr\u00e9s G\u00f3mez]]||{{flagicon|SWE}} Stefan Edberg <small>(4/6)</small>||{{flagicon|USA}} [[Pete Sampras]] <small>(1/14)</small>\n|-\n|'''[[1991 ATP Tour|1991]]'''||{{flagicon|GER}} Boris Becker <small>(5/6)</small>||{{flagicon|USA}} [[Jim Courier]] <small>(1/4)</small>||{{flagicon|GER}} [[Michael Stich]]||{{flagicon|SWE}} Stefan Edberg <small>(5/6)</small>\n|-\n|style=\"background:seashell\"|'''[[1992 ATP Tour|1992]]'''||style=\"background:seashell\"|{{flagicon|USA}} Jim Courier <small>(2/4)</small>||style=\"background:seashell\"|{{flagicon|USA}} Jim Courier <small>(3/4)</small>||{{flagicon|USA}} [[Andre Agassi]] <small>(1/8)</small>||{{flagicon|SWE}} Stefan Edberg <small>(6/6)</small>\n|-\n|style=\"background:seashell\"|'''[[1993 ATP Tour|1993]]'''||{{flagicon|USA}} Jim Courier <small>(4/4)</small>||{{flagicon|ESP}} [[Sergi Bruguera]] <small>(1/2)</small>||style=\"background:seashell\"|{{flagicon|USA}} Pete Sampras <small>(2/14)</small>||style=\"background:seashell\"|{{flagicon|USA}} Pete Sampras <small>(3/14)</small>\n|-\n|style=\"background:seashell\"|'''[[1994 ATP Tour|1994]]'''||style=\"background:seashell\"|{{flagicon|USA}} Pete Sampras <small>(4/14)</small>||{{flagicon|ESP}} Sergi Bruguera <small>(2/2)</small>||style=\"background:seashell\"|{{flagicon|USA}} Pete Sampras <small>(5/14)</small>||{{flagicon|USA}} Andre Agassi <small>(2/8)</small>\n|-\n|style=\"background:seashell\"|'''[[1995 ATP Tour|1995]]'''||{{flagicon|USA}} Andre Agassi <small>(3/8)</small>||{{flagicon|AUT}} [[Thomas Muster]]||style=\"background:seashell\"|{{flagicon|USA}} Pete Sampras <small>(6/14)</small>||style=\"background:seashell\"|{{flagicon|USA}} Pete Sampras <small>(7/14)</small>\n|-\n|'''[[1996 ATP Tour|1996]]'''||{{flagicon|Germany}} Boris Becker <small>(6/6)</small>||{{flagicon|RUS}} [[Yevgeny Kafelnikov]] <small>(1/2)</small>||{{flagicon|NED}} [[Richard Krajicek]]||{{flagicon|USA}} Pete Sampras <small>(8/14)</small>\n|-\n|style=\"background:seashell\"|'''[[1997 ATP Tour|1997]]'''||style=\"background:seashell\"|{{flagicon|USA}} Pete Sampras <small>(9/14)</small>||{{flagicon|BRA}} [[Gustavo Kuerten]] <small>(1/3)</small>||style=\